John Truong was babysitting 2-year-old Ronnie Tran on Tuesday night when his sister Alyssa Chang asked him to babysit the boy . 
  She told him the boy was her boyfriend's son and they wanted to go on a date night . 
  Chang and the boy's grandmother Vien Nguyen allegedly abducted the boy and his mother with the help of the grandmother . 
  An Amber Alert was issued for the boy after he was found safe . 
  Truong's sister has been arrested in connection to the kidnapping . 
 